                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>HTableUtil provides the following helper methods:&lt;br/&gt;
{code}&lt;br/&gt;
public static void bucketRsPut(HTable htable, List&amp;lt;Put&amp;gt; puts) throws IOException&lt;br/&gt;
{code}&lt;br/&gt;
It processes a List of Puts and writes them to an HTable instance in RegionServer buckets via the htable.put method.&lt;br/&gt;
{code}&lt;br/&gt;
public static void bucketRsBatch(HTable htable, List&amp;lt;Row&amp;gt; rows) throws IOException&lt;br/&gt;
{code}&lt;br/&gt;
Processes a List of Rows (Put, Delete) and writes them to an HTable instance in RegionServer buckets via the htable.batch method.</customfieldvalue>

